settings: "CMS": "Sanity", "THEME": "corporate1", "COMPONENT": "x"

STEP 1: Obtain reference knowledge as a guide.
    Source: Use the following components as a guide:
        "packages/headless-basics-components/src/theme/default/components/__[template]/"
