        "packages/headless-basics-components/src/theme/{THEME}/components/{COMPONENT}"
    Replace {COMPONENT} with the setting in lowercase and remove underscores and dashes.

STEP 2: Create Component Folder & Structure
    Create a folder named '{COMPONENT}' (lowercase) with a subfolder 'components/variants'.

STEP 3: Edit File: {COMPONENT}/components/variants/*.tsx

    Description: All variant files using StandardComponentProps.

