STEP 5: Edit File: {COMPONENT}/components/variants/data/upsertDemoData.ts

    Description: Query to upsert CMS data when fields are blank.   references context and fields obtains from images.

    Instructions:
        Runnable self contained node module, that inserts a new page and example component.
        Provide an example function like upsertDemoDataIfBlank.
